title: SB Chronicles Vol. 2: Luan Oliveira In Focus
description:
Nike SB pro Luan Oliveira speaks on his highly-anticipated next video part in SB Chronicles Vol. 2. 

Nike SB's new full-length video The SB Chronicles Vol. 2 hits iTunes on December 10th.

Check out http://www.SBChronicles.com for more information.
